data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers an abundance of space, comfort, and convenience. Enjoy ample space for your family and guests with five generously sized bedrooms. Three bathrooms provide convenience and ensure everyone has their own space to get ready. The primary bathroom features a SAUNA. Whether you need space for entertaining, family time, or creating a home office, this home offers three large living areas to suit your needs. The FOUR-CAR GARAGE has you covered. Store your vehicles, recreational equipment, or use it as a workshop. BRAND NEW METAL ROOF 2021. This home is perfect for a growing family, those who love to entertain, or anyone in need of space and comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home.
